Package com.gemalto.mfs.mwsdk.provisioning

Class ProvisioningServiceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gemalto.mfs.mwsdk.provisioning.ProvisioningServiceManager
  • public class ProvisioningServiceManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides the functionalities to build the connection between SDK & CPS, handles incoming message from CPS and takes an action inside SDK accordingly. This class is the main entry of the provisioning service component and provides the capability for developer to retrieve the following registered business service objects:
    1. EnrollingBusinessService
    2. ProvisioningBusinessService
